{"title":"Scroll of magic detection","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Scroll_of_magic_detection","type":"markdown","data":"| ? [![Scroll.png](/images/8/8d/Scroll.png)](/wiki/File:Scroll.png) |                                                               |\n| ----------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Name                                                              | detect magic                                                  |\n| Appearance                                                        | [random](/wiki/Randomised_appearance \"Randomised appearance\") |\n| Base price                                                        | 100 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                             |\n| Weight                                                            | 5                                                             |\n| Ink to write                                                      | [7-13](/wiki/Magic_marker \"Magic marker\")                     |\n| Monster use                                                       | *Will not be used by monsters.*                               |\n\n| ? [![Scroll.png](/images/8/8d/Scroll.png)](/wiki/File:Scroll.png) |                                                               |\n| ----------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Name                                                              | magic detection                                               |\n| Appearance                                                        | [random](/wiki/Randomised_appearance \"Randomised appearance\") |\n| Base price                                                        | 300 [zm](/wiki/Zorkmid \"Zorkmid\")                             |\n| Weight                                                            | 5                                                             |\n| Ink to write                                                      | [8-15](/wiki/Magic_marker \"Magic marker\")                     |\n| Monster use                                                       | *Will not be used by monsters.*                               |\n\nA **scroll of magic detection** is a type of [scroll](/wiki/Scroll \"Scroll\") that appears in [GruntHack](/wiki/GruntHack \"GruntHack\"), [EvilHack](/wiki/EvilHack \"EvilHack\") and [Hack'EM](/wiki/Hack%27EM \"Hack'EM\"). In GruntHack, it is known as a **scroll of detect magic** and has a base cost of 100[zm](/wiki/Zm \"Zm\"), while in EvilHack and Hack'EM the scroll has a base cost of 300zm.\n\n## Description\n\nWhen read, the scroll detects all [magical items](/wiki/Magical_item \"Magical item\") on the current level similar to a [potion of object detection](/wiki/Potion_of_object_detection \"Potion of object detection\"), including items with [object properties](/wiki/Object_properties \"Object properties\"), as well as revealing the current location of [monsters](/wiki/Monster \"Monster\") that are capable of casting [monster spells](/wiki/Monster_spell \"Monster spell\"). The exact effects of the scroll depend on its [beatitude](/wiki/Beatitude \"Beatitude\"): An uncursed scroll of detect magic will flag all revealed items as \"magical\", while a [blessed](/wiki/Blessed \"Blessed\") scroll will identify the item type and object properties of any detected magical items; a cursed scrolls will also detect [mimics](/wiki/Mimic \"Mimic\") and wakes up any monsters that it detects.\n\n- *This page is a **[stub](/wiki/Category:Stubs \"Category:Stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Scroll_of_magic_detection\\&action=edit)*\n\n[![This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.](/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"T