ml5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Scroll_of_magic_detection rootpage-Scroll_of_magic_detection skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Scroll of magic detection</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-white\">?</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Scroll.png\" src=\"/images/8/8d/Scroll.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<td>detect magic\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Randomised_appearance\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Randomised appearance\">random</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>100 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td>5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ink to write\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Magic_marker\" title=\"Magic marker\">7-13</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Monster use\n</th>\n<td><small><i>Will not be used by monsters.</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-white\">?</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Scroll.png\" src=\"/images/8/8d/Scroll.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<td>magic detection\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Randomised_appearance\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Randomised appearance\">random</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>300 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td>5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Ink to write\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Magic_marker\" title=\"Magic marker\">8-15</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Monster use\n</th>\n<td><small><i>Will not be used by monsters.</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>A <b>scroll of magic detection</b> is a type of <a href=\"/wiki/Scroll\" title=\"Scroll\">scroll</a> that appears in <a href=\"/wiki/GruntHack\" title=\"GruntHack\">GruntHack</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>. In GruntHack, it is known as a <b>scroll of detect magic</b> and has a base cost of 100<a href=\"/wiki/Zm\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm\">zm</a>, while in EvilHack and Hack'EM the scroll has a base cost of 300zm.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>When read, the scroll detects all <a href=\"/wiki/Magical_item\" title=\"Magical item\">magical items</a> on the current level similar to a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_object_detection\" title=\"Potion of object detection\">potion of object detection</a>, including items with <a href=\"/wiki/Object_properties\" title=\"Object properties\">object properties</a>, as well as revealing the current location of <a href=\"/wiki/Monster\" title=\"Monster\">monsters</a> that are capable of casting <a href=\"/wiki/Monster_spell\" title=\"Monster spell\">monster spells</a>. The exact effects of the scroll depend on its <a href=\"/wiki/Beatitude\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Beatitude\">beatitude</a>: An uncursed scroll of detect magic will flag all revealed items as \"magical\", while a <a href=\"/wiki/Blessed\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Blessed\">blessed</a> scroll will identify the item type and object properties of any detected magical items; a cursed scrolls will also detect <a href=\"/wiki/Mimic\" title=\"Mimic\">mimics</a> and wakes up any monsters that it detects.\n</p>\n<div class=\"stub\">\n<dl><dd><i>This page is a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">stub</a></b>. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Scroll_of_magic_detection&amp;action=edit\"><b>expanding this page</b>.</a></i></dd></dl>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926190303\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.037 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 133/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 728/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2531/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 301/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   16.705      1 -total\n 48.64%    8.126      1 Template:Variant-343\n 3